Provide players with some data in their personal Zgirls account in real time:

 1.Resources (Fuel, Food, Steel, Alloy, Obisidian, Kyanite, Kyanite basic, Kyanite Cluster, Glory Mark, Catalyst, Diamond)

 2.The levels of the four mechas

 3.The number of three types landmine (grenades, mines, incendiary)

 4.Number of troops (only the first 10 types of troops with the largest number are displayed)

 5.^Progress (display unit name, number of training, remaining training time, total training time)

 6.^Activated Star Language (display the active Star Language name and required Star Stone combine)

 7.Enablers (only display Enablers level)

 +Remarks:

 I.The data items with \^\ are still negotiated by Zgirls development department and have not been put into service, please pay attention. 

 II.In order to reducing the data traffic consumed by ZGT, the eal-time\ update part of this function will be automatically updated every three seconds.

 III.You can adjust the required additional functions through the settings page (the gear button on the main page) (allows to read the player's data in the Zgirls account, display the resource type data transition, show/hide the specified category display, data value, etc. )

 IV.Please make sure that the device is connected to valid Wi-Fi /open mobile data before using the real-time data list.

 V.The real-time data list can only work normally when Zgirls version 1.2.21 (or later) is installed, otherwise it will crash.
